            "content": [
              {
                "nodeType": "text",
                "value": "Sleight of Hand is the mastery of quick, deceptive movements, blending physical dexterity with minor magical illusions. It\u2019s used to palm objects, perform tricks, or conceal small items like daggers or spell scrolls. In a fantasy setting, it might involve vanishing coins, swapping potions, or subtly casting cantrips unnoticed. This expertise shines for rogues, performers, and enchanters who rely on misdirection to outwit foes or dazzle crowds.",
                "marks": [],
                "data": {}
              }
            ]
